{"tid":338542,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"每月一次既board game 聚會 (第六次聚會啦)","createTime":"2017-07-28T09:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T04:36:52.000Z","uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a022bbab1b1091b32016a26583bf61348535937","tid":338542,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T09:28:43.000Z","msg":"黎緊會係第六次聚會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地主要以一齊玩Board Game 為主 (多數玩一d 可以大家一齊笑既game，有時用小小腦既game，次次唔同。例如，牛頭王，矮人掘金等，仲會有好多好多類型既)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多數每次都會有d 新遊戲同新朋友，所以一定會教大家玩同埋有d 小遊戲比大家認識一下先。其實大家重點唔係board game，都係想一齊玩下only。<br />\n<br />\n試過去board game cafe，但最近都係book活動室玩，多d 私人空間無咁嘈。<br />\n<br />\n每次預around 12人。利申：年齡18-22左右 (希望保持隊形)<br />\n<br />\n我地都係一班平時無fd子，放假放學放工無乜朋友所以好悶，大毒小毒既人，單拖同有朋友一齊黎都無問題。<br />\n<br />\n再利申：我地都係較為靜同內向，唔係太識social，所以board game 幾岩我地互動。同埋board game 可以有d 目標咁同人有多d 交流，好岩內向既你，慢慢都會訓練到自己。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有興趣就留低contact。第六次聚會會係黎緊星期五晚 (4/8)，已booked個活動室會準備3個board game 比大家玩。<br />\n<br />\n報名link<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSePvo37Fw22bx6wczAr8O7ZF5Lif6Wwvq_e94w3wm_OpimxFQ/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSePvo37Fw22bx6wczAr8O7ZF5Lif6Wwvq_e94w3wm_OpimxFQ%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=WB9wSc5z1ZO9upoRyOJmuY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=9115ae80\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSePvo37Fw22bx6wczAr8O7ZF5Lif6Wwvq_e94w3wm_OpimxFQ/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n注意：之前玩開既已有一埋人報左會黎，所以得番幾個位。<br />\n<br />\n上幾次都收到大量巴絲報名，但飛機率有d 高，樓主有小小嬲嬲豬，請大家睇清楚日子！！plz<br />\n<br />\n回帶：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/309112/page/1?post=914c24e3467baf35672fa3ea337ae86bea67808a\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/309112/page/1?post=914c24e3467baf35672fa3ea337ae86bea67808a</a>"},{"pid":"9561761d3900cdc6a596a09f26fe2088a55aa4fa","tid":338542,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T10:03:20.000Z","msg":"太多人玩悶到瞓著，6至8人max啦"},{"pid":"9fb624eea828ca8cbbe8c4c64c956c28c218e063","tid":338542,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:32:49.000Z","msg":"上次個個聲稱自己毒撚 ，點知去到成班MK潮童 ，著晒MND <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我唔敢再去了"},{"pid":"aacdd4cde23a522449fa4358921855b29bbaf351","tid":338542,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次個個聲稱自己毒撚 ，點知去到成班MK潮童 ，著晒MND <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我唔敢再去了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上次唔見你既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e608bd3ddc11af5484dae832e72f1051bc5ab025","tid":338542,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:24:49.000Z","msg":"有啲興趣，但主要會玩啲乜game，男女比例主要係點，會唔會好多mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28e8d231472c5d1d6c1db92206f9053fa24fa6d","tid":338542,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲興趣，但主要會玩啲乜game，男女比例主要係點，會唔會好多mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n保證無mk. (真係未試過有）<br />\n但可以肯定係 仔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e51e3607bb442b06d33d6b046a575395d3852dd","tid":338542,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T15:51:07.000Z","msg":"推一推先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96e41ad09970e34373aeb